      "date": "2011-10-19 12:42:05.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3: (2 inline comments)\n\nI know patch is merged but in fact it doesn't fix both issues correctly. \n\nThere is patch for kmem_init() fix in http://review.whamcloud.com/586 but for some reason Maloo didn't respond on it for a long time. It fixes lu_kmem_init() itself so it frees all caches if failed. I am not sure about another change - do lu_kmem_init() before class_type_init(), need more details from Jinshan.\n\nAs for test 180a, the problem is not awk but our lprocfs_rd_import() which must be fixed.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 3
    },
